00:13:21.220 --> 00:13:24.100
And that's sort of the Dagster sort of pitch, right?

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:31.040
Like if you want to understand the things that are being produced by these tasks, tell us about the underlying assets.

00:13:32.040 --> 00:13:36.000
