00:22:45.140 --> 00:22:49.340
It stands for a bunch of things that are not connected in a circle, but are connected in some way.

00:22:49.660 --> 00:22:51.180
So there can't be any loops, right?

00:22:51.280 --> 00:22:52.820
Because then you never know where to start or where to end.

