Not a circle.

00:22:58.580 --> 00:23:01.200
As long as there's like a path through this data set

00:23:01.480 --> 00:23:02.540
with the beginning and an end,

00:23:03.080 --> 00:23:08.340
then we can kind of start to model this connected graph of things.

