00:23:14.840 --> 00:23:16.380
And then we can either branch off in parallel

00:23:16.640 --> 00:23:19.560
or we can continue linearly until everything is complete.

00:23:19.960 --> 00:23:23.020
And if something breaks in the middle, we can resume from that broken spot.

